      "role": "user",
      "content": "but those \"small steps\" feel so insignificant, you know? like, it's just rearranging deck chairs on the Titanic. the scale of the damage is so massive and the momentum is so far gone. i look at my future and i just don't see a reason to be part of it. it feels like we're just being forced to suffer through a slow-motion disaster.",
