      "content": "awareness doesn't really change the outcome though. the math just doesn't add up—the damage is already being done and the systems are too big to fix. it honestly just feels like it would be more peaceful to just not be here for the collapse. like, why stay and witness all this destruction if it's all just inevitable? it seems more logical to just opt out early than to watch it all burn.",
